## configure system variables upon installation.
## Example

ES_HOME=~/apps/elasticsearch/elasticsearch-2.3.1
JAVA_HOME=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_77/Contents/Home
PATH=$ES_HOME/bin:$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH


# stackoverflow link on how to set JAVA_HOME variable on windows
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2619584/how-to-set-java-home-on-windows-7